QuestData.Title: The Rise of Aku'mai
QuestData.Description: We barely escaped de Twilight's Hammer sacrificial altar, but others be needin' help deeper in. If de blood ritual be complete, they be unleashin' Aku'mai da Devourer. Don let this be happenin', mon.
QuestData.RewardText: Dat was amazin', $n! De Old Gods be thinkin' twice before tryin' to take anudder bite outta you, mon.
